<!doctype html>
    <html>
      <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>Reminder Message Previews</title>
        <style>
          body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #111827; line-height: 1.45; }
          h1 { font-size: 26px; }
          h2 { font-size: 21px; margin-top: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 6px; }
          h3 { font-size: 16px; margin-top: 18px; color: #0f766e; }
          .meta { background: #f3f4f6; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding: 12px; margin: 12px 0 20px; }
          .message { border: 1px solid #d1d5db; background: #ffffff; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0 16px; }
          .muted { color: #6b7280; }
        </style>
      </head>
      <body>
        <h1>Reminder Message Previews - Email, WhatsApp, SMS</h1>
        <div class="meta">
          <p><b>Company:</b> University of Delhi</p>
          <p><b>Config owner used by current shared generator:</b> Aman kumar Sah (super_admin)</p>
          <p><b>Generated:</b> 17/6/2026, 10:18:24 am</p>
          <p><b>Preview assumption:</b> CD eligible customer, no older unpaid invoice, sample invoice amount ₹25,000.00.</p>
          <p><b>Important:</b> These previews apply the same template fill and automatic payment-summary append logic used by the sending code.</p>
        </div>
        
    <h2>30 Day - 30 Day Reminder</h2>
    <p>
      <b>Active in current shared generation:</b> Yes<br>
      <b>CD used in preview:</b> 2% within 30 days<br>
      <b>Note:</b> This rule is available to the current shared reminder generator.
    </p>
    
          <h3>Email (enabled)</h3>
          <p><b>Subject/label:</b> Payment reminder: invoice INV-30-001 now at 30 days</p>
          <div class="message">Dear Accounts Team,<br><br>This is a reminder for invoice INV-30-001 dated 18 May 2026 for Sample Dealer Pvt Ltd with pending amount ₹25,000.00.<br>Reference number: REF-30-001.<br><br>The bill has now aged 30 days, and this reminder was triggered by your day 30 rule.<br><br>Since no older unpaid bill is pending for your account, we are giving you CD of 2% if this invoice is cleared within 30 days.<br><br>If payment is already scheduled, please ignore this note. Otherwise, feel free to reply if you need any supporting documents.<br><br>Regards,<br>University of Delhi<br><br>Payment Summary:<br>Current invoice due: ₹25,000.00<br>Previous due: ₹0.00<br>Total due: ₹25,000.00</div>
        
          <h3>WhatsApp (enabled)</h3>
          <p><b>Subject/label:</b> 30 Day Reminder reminder</p>
          <div class="message">Hello Accounts Team, invoice INV-30-001 for Sample Dealer Pvt Ltd has pending amount ₹25,000.00. Ref: REF-30-001. The bill is now 30 days old. Since no older unpaid bill is pending, we are giving you CD of 2% if paid within 30 days. Current invoice due: ₹25,000.00. Previous due: ₹0.00. Total due: ₹25,000.00.</div>
        
          <h3>SMS (disabled / not sent unless enabled)</h3>
          <p><b>Subject/label:</b> 30 Day Reminder reminder</p>
          <div class="message">Reminder: invoice INV-30-001 for Sample Dealer Pvt Ltd has pending amount ₹25,000.00. Ref: REF-30-001. The bill is now 30 days old. Since no older unpaid bill is pending, we are giving you CD of 2% if paid within 30 days. Current invoice due: ₹25,000.00. Previous due: ₹0.00. Total due: ₹25,000.00.</div>
        
  
